━━━ Experiment 2/20 ━━━
**Experiment 2 result: 66.0 (KEPT)**

The angle blending fix improved the score from 47.0 → 66.0 (+40%). The bug was causing the creature to sometimes steer in completely the wrong direction when angles wrapped around ±π. With proper angular interpolation via `atan2(sin, cos)`, the creature now consistently steers toward food and away from hazards correctly.

